# Apache Publishing

Repository published through Apache Alias configuration.

Current aliases

```
/rpms
/images
/manifests
```

Commands used

```
sudo tee /etc/httpd/conf.d/linuxinfra-repo.conf

sudo chmod -R a+rX /srv/repo

sudo restorecon -Rv /srv/repo

sudo systemctl restart httpd
```

---

# Repo Client

Current tool

```
use-local-repo.sh
```

Purpose

Converts a Rocky Linux VM into a repository client.

Functions

* Backup repo files
* Disable public repositories
* Configure local repository
* Refresh DNF
* Verify repository

Used before LinuxInfra on client VMs.

