# Project Design Principles

Infrastructure first.

Applications second.

Everything reproducible.

Everything script driven.

Every server starts from a clean Rocky Linux installation.

Snapshots are taken after each validated milestone.

Repository VM is built first.

All remaining servers use the Repository VM for package installation.

Every build is verified before moving to the next phase.

